OpenU IL Extended Forum Layout
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

----------------------------------------------------
Description
----------------------------------------------------

Enclosed is an extended module for the Moodle forum activity (see screenshot).


----------------------------------------------------
Installation Information
----------------------------------------------------

Copy "extendedforum" directory to moodle/mod.


----------------------------------------------------
Notes
----------------------------------------------------

It is advisable to have the OpenU IL theme installed so that the layout will work properly. If you have it installed
you will not need to do step 3 above.


